message:
feat: add termweb SDK for building terminal apps

Electron-like API for rendering web apps in terminal:
- app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain (high-level)
- CDP, KittyGraphics, Terminal (mid-level)
- spawn, getBinaryPath (low-level)

Example usage:
  const { app, BrowserWindow } = require('termweb');
  app.on('ready', () => {
    const win = new BrowserWindow();
    win.loadURL('https://example.com');
  });

